Class BigRational

java.lang.Object
Q18.BigRational
public class BigRational
extends java.lang.Object
Project: DataStructuresMidterm Package: Q18

Author:
Ibrahim Basar YARGICI Date 12/1/2020

Q18-g) Modify the BigRational class to store a MathContext that can be initialized from an additional BigRational constructor(or which defaults to MathContext.UNLIMITED). Then add a toBigDecimal method to the BigRational class.
